OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FHungary's prime minister Viktor Orban
OL,8,Fhas been ousted after 16 years in
OL,9,Fpower, with Peter Magyar's pro-
OL,10,FEuropean Tisza party on track to win a
OL,11,Ftwo-thirds majority in Parliament.
OL,13,FThe bombshell election results could
OL,14,Fhave global repercussions,
OL,15,Fparticularly among far-right movements
OL,16,Fwhich have viewed Orban as a beacon
OL,17,Ffor nationalist populism.
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@drpqD@NrrxD@Vrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
