OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FWith 98% of votes counted as of around
OL,8,F4am local time, Hungary's electoral
OL,9,Fauthorities said the Tisza party had
OL,10,Fwon 138 seats.
OL,12,FThis would give the party, a member of
OL,13,Fthe European Union's centre-right,
OL,14,Fliberal conservative European People's
OL,15,FParty, more than two-thirds of the
OL,16,Fseats required for a supermajority,
OL,17,Fwhich would allow it to amend
OL,18,FHungary's constitution and pass
OL,19,Flegislation effectively.
OL,26,@kD@Vrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
