OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FHungarian voters appeared to have
OL,8,Frejected the authoritarian policies
OL,9,Fand global far-right movement that
OL,10,FOrban embodied during his 16 years in
OL,11,Fpower.
OL,13,FOrban, a close ally of US President
OL,14,FDonald Trump and Russian President
OL,15,FVladimir Putin, quickly conceded
OL,16,Fdefeat on Sunday night in what he
OL,17,Fcalled a "painful" election result.
OL,26,@kD@VrprD@DrpuD@Drp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
