CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,F"I congratulated the victorious
OL,8,Fparty, Orban told followers. "We are
OL,9,Fgoing to serve the Hungarian nation
OL,10,Fand our homeland from opposition.
OL,12,FUS Vice President JD Vance had made a
OL,13,Fvisit to Hungary just days earlier,
OL,14,Fmeant to help push Orban over the
OL,15,Ffinish line.
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@AOUpD@LrppD@_OUvD@Wrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
