OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FElection victor Magyar, a former Orban
OL,8,Floyalist who campaigned against
OL,9,Fcorruption and on everyday issues like
OL,10,Fhealthcare and public transport, has
OL,11,Fpledged to rebuild Hungary's
OL,12,Frelationships with the European Union
OL,13,Fand NATO ` ties that frayed under
OL,14,FOrban.
OL,16,FHis victory was expected to transform
OL,17,Fpolitical dynamics within the EU,
OL,18,Fwhere Orban had upended the bloc by
OL,19,Ffrequently vetoing key decisions,
OL,20,Fprompting concerns he sought to break
OL,21,Fit up from the inside.
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@erpvD@DrpzD@Jrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FIt will also reverberate among far-
OL,8,Fright movements around the world,
OL,9,Fwhich have viewed Orban as a beacon
OL,10,Ffor how nationalist populism can be
OL,11,Fused to wage culture wars and leverage
OL,12,Fstate power to undermine opponents.
OL,14,FTens of thousands of jubilant
OL,15,Fsupporters gathered along the Danube
OL,16,Friver as Magyar delivered a speech,
OL,17,Ftelling his voters they had rewritten
OL,18,FHungarian history.
OL,26,@kD@VrpqD@Vrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
