OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,F"Tonight, truth prevailed over lies.
OL,8,FToday, we won because Hungarians
OL,9,Fdidn't ask what their homeland could
OL,10,Fdo for them ` they asked what they
OL,11,Fcould do for their homeland," he said.
OL,13,F"You found the answer. And you
OL,14,Ffollowed through."
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@AOUsD@]O]uD@AOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
