PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FIn an interview with The Associated
OL,8,FPress earlier this month, Magyar said
OL,9,Fthe election will be a "referendum" on
OL,10,Fwhether Hungary continues on its drift
OL,11,Ftoward Russia under Orban, or can
OL,12,Fretake its place among the democratic
OL,13,Fsocieties of Europe.
OL,15,FOn the streets of Budapest, drivers
OL,16,Fblared car horns and cranked up anti-
OL,17,Fgovernment songs while people marching
OL,18,Fin the streets chanted and screamed.
OL,26,@kD@VrpqD@XOUqD@cO]sD@Xrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
