FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FMany revellers chanted "Ruszkik haza!"
OL,8,For "Russians go home!" ` a phrase used
OL,9,Fwidely during Hungary's 1956 anti-
OL,10,FSoviet revolution, and which had
OL,11,Fgained increasing currency amid
OL,12,FOrban's drift toward Moscow.
OL,14,FTurnout in the election was nearly
OL,15,F80%, according to the National
OL,16,FElection Office, a record number in
OL,17,Fany vote in Hungary's post-Communist
OL,18,Fhistory.
OL,20,F'Choice between East or West'
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@XOUoD@fO]pD@DOUpD@VO]tD@Drp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
