PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FOrban, the EU's longest-serving leader
OL,8,Fand one of its biggest antagonists,
OL,9,Ftravelled a long road from his early
OL,10,Fdays as a liberal, anti-Soviet
OL,11,Ffirebrand to the Russia-friendly
OL,12,Fnationalist admired today by the
OL,13,Fglobal far-right.
OL,15,FThe EU will be waiting to see how
OL,16,FMagyar changes Hungary's approach to
OL,17,FUkraine.
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@Drp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FOrban repeatedly frustrated EU efforts
OL,8,Fto support the neighbouring country in
OL,9,Fits war against Russia's full-scale
OL,10,Finvasion, while cultivating close ties
OL,11,Fto Putin and refusing to end Hungary's
OL,12,Fdependence on Russian energy imports.
OL,14,FRecent reporting has shown a top
OL,15,Fmember of Orban's government
OL,16,Ffrequently shared the contents of EU
OL,17,Fdiscussions with Moscow, raising
OL,18,Faccusations that Hungary was acting on
OL,19,FRussia's behalf within the bloc.
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@DrpwD@Nrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FDuring his 16 years in power, Orban
OL,8,Flaunched harsh crackdowns on minority
OL,9,Frights and media freedoms, subverted
OL,10,Fmany of Hungary's institutions, and
OL,11,Fhas been accused of siphoning large
OL,12,Fsums of money into the coffers of his
OL,13,Fallied business elite, an allegation
OL,14,Fhe denies.
OL,16,FHe heavily strained Hungary's
OL,17,Frelationship with the EU ` repeatedly
OL,18,Fusing his veto to block decisions that
OL,19,Frequire unanimity.
OL,26,@kD@VrpoD@brp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FMost recently, he blocked a 90billion
OL,8,Feuro (around #78.5 billion) EU loan to
OL,9,FUkraine, prompting his partners to
OL,10,Faccuse him of hijacking the critical
OL,11,Faid.
OL,13,FMembers of Trump's "Make America Great
OL,14,FAgain" movement are among those who
OL,15,Fsee Orban's government and his Fidesz
OL,16,Fpolitical party as shining examples of
OL,17,Fconservative, anti-globalist politics
OL,18,Fin action, while he is reviled by
OL,19,Fadvocates of liberal democracy and the
OL,20,Frule of law.
OL,26,@kD@VrpuD@TOUvD@FO]wD@Hrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
