CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FIn Budapest, Marcell Mehringer, 21,
OL,8,Fsaid he was voting "primarily so that
OL,9,FHungary will finally be a so-called
OL,10,FEuropean country, and so that young
OL,11,Fpeople, and really everyone, will do
OL,12,Ftheir fundamental civic duty to unite
OL,13,Fthis nation a bit and to breakdown
OL,14,Fthese boundaries borne of hatred".
