OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FMagyar faced a tough fight on his
OL,8,Fhands, as Orban had transformed
OL,9,FHungary's public media into a
OL,10,Fmouthpiece for his party, and vast
OL,11,Fswathes of the private media market
OL,12,Fgive him an advantage in spreading his
OL,13,Fmessage.
OL,15,FThe unilateral transformation of
OL,16,FHungary's electoral system and
OL,17,Fgerrymandering of its 106 voting
OL,18,Fdistricts by Fidesz also required
OL,19,FTisza to gain an estimated 5% more
OL,20,Fvotes than Orban's party to achieve a
OL,21,Fsimple majority.
OL,26,@kD@VrppD@Nrp|D@Orp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
