PN,31016
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776082266
OL,3,CHungary election: Orban ousted after
OL,4,C16 years as Peter Magyar wins huge
OL,5,Cmajority
OL,7,FAdditionally, hundreds of thousands of
OL,8,Fethnic Hungarians in neighbouring
OL,9,Fcountries had the right to vote in
OL,10,FHungarian elections and traditionally
OL,11,Fhave voted overwhelmingly for Orban's
OL,12,Fparty.
OL,14,FRussian secret services have plotted
OL,15,Fto interfere and tip the election in
OL,16,FOrban's favor, according to numerous
OL,17,Fmedia reports including by The
OL,18,FWashington Post.
OL,26,@kD@VrpsD@brpxD@Drp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
